replyContent:
Unfortunately that is a known issue of Android KitKat. The bug is present if text size is greater than 256px (absolut).
There are three possibilities:
- Disable the stroke effect on the page Settings / Text
- Make the watermark smaller
- Create an image watermark like yours in an image editor like Photoshop or Gimp and use it
